      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**[\ud83c\udfcb Sprint Health](/d/jira-sprint-health)**  \u2014 Velocity, delivery %, scope changes\n\n**[\u23f1 Flow & Cycle Time](/d/jira-flow-cycle-time)**  \u2014 RFT\u2192Done, throughput, WIP\n\n**[\ud83d\udc1b Quality & Bugs](/d/jira-quality-bugs)**  \u2014 Bug rates, priorities, releases\n\n**[\ud83d\udc65 Team Overview](/d/jira-team-overview)**  \u2014 Per-assignee metrics"
